\end_inset

 such as spin.
 It follows directly from the composite notation that 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{\boldsymbol{i}}=\sum_{s_{i}}\sum_{i}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta_{\boldsymbol{i}\boldsymbol{j}}=\delta_{ij}\delta_{s_{i}s_{j}}$
\end_inset

.
 
